title: Great App!
content: I really enjoy using this app. It's very user-friendly and has all the features I need.

title: Needs Improvement
content: The app crashes frequently when I try to open it. Please fix this issue.

title: Feature Request
content: It would be great if you could add a dark mode to the app.

title: Excellent Support
content: The customer support team was very helpful and resolved my issue quickly.

title: Bug Report
content: There is a bug in the notification system. I am not receiving any alerts.

title: Love the New Update
content: The latest update has some great new features. Keep up the good work!

title: Slow Performance
content: The app takes a long time to load. Please work on improving the performance.

title: Suggestion
content: Can you add a way to customize the app's interface? It would be very helpful.
